  Maven home: /opt/maven
  MHD = /opt/maven [ M2_HOME ]:

export M2_HOME=/opt/maven
export PATH=$PATH:$M2_HOME/bin

sudo vi ~/.bash_profile
source ~/.bash_profile
MHD = /opt/maven 
The MHD is where the maven software is extracted.
